name: Etenp
description:
(This game was made for the Juice Jam)

Etenp is a plataformer game where you can't stop moving...

- Controls -

- AD or Right Left to move

- Space to jump

- R to restart the level

- N to skip level

- T (in the title screen) to activate the timer (disables the option to skip levels)

And thanks to Pato26 for general minor help
